# Safe BigQuery access

When querying BigQuery, use the `safe-bq` CLI instead of raw `bq`:

```
safe-bq query "SELECT ..."
safe-bq query -f path/to/query.sql
```

This ensures SELECT-only queries, allowlist enforcement, and audit logging. Do not use `bq query` directly for agent-initiated queries.
